                        <interp inst="t18700711-name-545" type="given" value="MATTHIAS"></interp>MATTHIAS SHARPE</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">recalled</hi>). I know the last witness well—I was at the examination at the Police Court—he was there—I spoke to him, and he said "What are you going to do with Heunessy," meaning Anderson.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18700711-name-546" type="witnessName">
