                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">recalled</hi>). I was at the examination before the Migis-trate—I saw Banks in Court, in company with a woman of the name of Hennessy.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18700711-name-547" type="witnessName">
